{{Main|2008 World Wheelchair Curling Championship}}
The '''qualification event''' for the '''[[2008 World Wheelchair Curling Championship]]''' was held from November 5 to 9, 2007 in [[Inverness]], [[Scotland]]. The event's two top finishers, Germany and China, both qualified to participate in the 2008 World Wheelchair Curling Championship. The two qualification spots were given to the top two teams at the conclusion of the [[Round-robin tournament|round robin]].

