{{Infobox bandy team | team = Broberg/Söderhamn Bandy | logo = Broberg Soderhamn IF logo.gif | founded = {{Start date and age|1919|df=yes}} | league = [[Elitserien (bandy)|Elitserien]] | division = | arena = [[Hällåsen]] | city = [[Söderhamn]], Sweden | coach = [[Ola Grönberg]] | website = {{URL|brobergsoderhamn.se}} <!-- Home --> |pattern_he1 = |pattern_la1 = |pattern_b1 = |pattern_ra1 = |pattern_sh1 = |pattern_so1 = |leftarm1 = FBF038 |body1 = FBF038 |rightarm1 = FBF038 |shorts1 = 000000 <!-- Away --> |pattern_he2 = |pattern_la2 = |pattern_b2 = |pattern_ra2 = |pattern_sh2 = |pattern_so2 = |leftarm2 =000000 |body2 =000000 |rightarm2 =000000 |shorts2 =000000 }}
'''Broberg/Söderhamn Bandy''' is a [[Sweden|Swedish]] [[bandy]] club from [[Söderhamn]] who play in the [[Elitserien (bandy)|Elitserien]]. Broberg/Söderhamn, also known as Brobergs IF, were founded in 1919. Broberg play their home matches at Hällåsen.
Broberg have won the [[Bandy World Cup]] 4 times in 1975, 1977, 1978 and 1983. They have also been runners-up twice in 1974 and 1981. They have also won the [[List of Swedish bandy champions|Swedish Championship]] final five times in 1947, 1963, 1964, 1976 and 1977.<ref> http://www.svenskbandy.se/BANDYFINALEN/HISTORIK/Svenskamastare/Herrar/</ref>
==History== Broberg/Söderhamn Bandy was founded in 1919.<ref>http://www.bandypuls.se/bandy/elitserien/broberg-soderhamns-trupp</ref>
