==2009 Event== The 2009 finals were on 14 and 15 July 2009 at [[Glenarm Castle]]. The event was sponsored by [[Met-Rx]].<ref>[http://www.ironmind.com/ironmind/opencms/archives.html?uri=/Articles/2009/Jun/ Ironmind June 2009 archives]</ref> The event was overseen by the [[Earl of Antrim]], who gave away The Devastator trophy.<ref>[http://www.ironmind.com/ironmind/opencms/archives.html?uri=/Articles/2009/Jul/ Ironmind July 2009 archives]</ref>
